long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
By clicking "Add to Chrome", I accept and agree to install "InsideTasks" Chrome extension and hereby agree to change default search to InsideTasks Search provided by the service, and I agree to the Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.

How to use:
Type preferred search term into the Google Chrome Omnibox. The InsideTasks Default Search Search will provide exceptional custom search results powered by Bing.
For more technical details you can read about Google Chrome API for Google Chrome Extensions.

You may remove this extension at any time from the chrome extension page.
